{"tid":644212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(中共又一陰謀受質疑)英國會議議員質疑:為何還要花錢援助支那","createTime":"2018-04-27T05:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T10:57:06.000Z","uid":99205,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2ccdf48ab1fdcf58dced4d44dee3abb98b09cd2e","tid":644212,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/27/EucMoB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2FEucMoB.jpg&h=98c96ba5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n近日，英國一位議員批評英國政府現在仍然在向全球第二大經濟體&mdash;&mdash;中國提供援助，她認為英國這樣做毫無意義。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n發表上述言論的是保守黨議員Pauline Latham，她在4月25日的議會會議上對英國商務大臣Sam Gyimah提出質疑，為何要給一個自己還有許多對外援助計劃的國家投入大筆資金。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n英國政府多年前曾表示將不再給中國提供援助。其中，英國國際開發部（The Department for International Development）自2011年起已經停止了對華援助項目，但最新數據顯示，英國政府的其他部門在2016年向中國提供了4690萬英鎊的援助，比 前一年增加了260萬鎊。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n英國的援助計劃包括改善中國青島市的癡呆症護理條件，還有一個鼓勵兒童減少鹽攝入的校園計劃。<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLatham稱，英國的商業、能源和工業戰略部門占到對華援助的大部分支出，她說：「我真的不明白，我們為什麼在中國花這麼多錢。這可是4690萬英鎊，此前我曾被告知，我們國家並沒有援助中國。他們是快速發展的大國，夜以繼日地建設城市和機場。為什麼我們還要給他們花這麼多錢？」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n有政府官員試圖以人道立場解釋英國如何令中國的孩子更安全，例如助中國引入新型孕婦護理設備，用於預測婦女懷孕期間的併發症風險，但被Latham打斷：「為什麼他們不能安全的養育孩子？為什麼我們必須要為這樣的事情付錢？」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n她續道：「我真不明白為什麼英國要花這個錢。他們自己還有援助別人的計劃，那為什麼他們不把自己管好？」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://hkjam.com/?p=10629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkjam.com%2F%3Fp%3D10629&d=51wRGTyfgKGB8ujbjWhh8fiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=61346e94\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkjam.com/?p=10629</a>"},{"pid":"c702b35007baca94119d7047e4937132562a1d5a","tid":644212,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:51:20.000Z","msg":"白痴英國"},{"pid":"91751337d9d76ffb67a4cd6dc25638b2fd48626b","tid":644212,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"32388f64e9ddac11992b52e3ff0239d9f8c8937b","tid":644212,"uid":99205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:53:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.express.co.uk/news/politics/951540/foreign-aid-china-uk-pauline-latham-sam-gyimah/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.express.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2F951540%2Fforeign-aid-china-uk-pauline-latham-sam-gyimah%2Famp&d=51wRGTyfgKGB8ujbjWhh8fiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ffdef785\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.express.co.uk/news/politics/951540/foreign-aid-china-uk-pauline-latham-sam-gyimah/amp</a><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/27/135337_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F135337_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=838cea68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMs Latham raged at Sam Gyimah when the Education minister defended spending an eye-watering &pound;46.9million on projects in China.<br />\n<br />\nMr Gyimah reasoned six per cent of the world&rsquo;s poorest live in China before adding the mind-boggling amount of dosh from the pockets of hard-working Britons is being ploughed into screening tests to predict the risk of complications in Chinese pregnancies, prompting a red mist to descend over Ms Latham.<br />\n<br />\nShe said: &ldquo;Why can&rsquo;t they work out how to have babies safely? Why are we having to pay for things like that?<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;They have got their own aid programme. So why can they not look after their own?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nDuring the spat at the Commons International Development Committee, she pointed out wealthy China is &ldquo;building airports by the dozen&rdquo; in sprawling new cities before slamming the Government for breaking its pledge to send foreign aid to the country.<br />\n<br />\nThe bickering follows shocking news that foreign fishermen are scooping millions of pounds in UK Government aid.<br />\n<br />\nAid from the UK has funded fishing projects all over the world, including Nigeria, Malawi, Nepal and Zimbabwe.<br />\n<br />\nThe news comes as the Government is accused of betraying British fishermen by failing to take control of UK waters after Brexit, as promised by the Leave campaign"},{"pid":"679a725dbc6afb97ee070a214ff783358799ab35","tid":644212,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c33d4ba3d8efc3426534cc962aa0dff658f460c","tid":644212,"uid":99205,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:57:39.000Z","msg":"基於紳士風度及人道理由，英美多年都幫助支那<br />\n<br />\n結果點大家有目共睹<br />\n<br />\n而家支x仲派不少細作週圍去，又賄賂不少國家議員進行各種政治步署"},{"pid":"a1164c31b8c333150112cb6f88e94c4bf62cb6a5","tid":644212,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:58:58.000Z","msg":"中降頭"},{"pid":"5bd8de20de62423bfd3cb96a2bc33710b5d9d961","tid":644212,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:00:00.000Z","msg":"中國又贏屌"},{"pid":"50407fb6c2c8625015d32ecd374ebb7885ec7afc","tid":644212,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:01:01.000Z","msg":"我有種其實係俾緊陀地費嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0dde62586ade8b06946692c7b1ccf2a9363d45","tid":644212,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27dfba4ea49f5f4bbe3ea7121f6d74968960e54a","tid":644212,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:22:55.000Z","msg":"中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14dab3595f986cfb1d704c7ad06fff8ba082a7b","tid":644212,"uid":113626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:23:51.000Z","msg":"黃種人社會本來就係要